<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es" data-theme="system">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>YiQi ERP — API Docs</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Plus+Jakarta+Sans:wght@700;800&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=IBM+Plex+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="./site.css">
<script src="./components/site-header.js" defer></script>
<script src="./components/site-footer.js" defer></script>
<style>
[data-theme="light"] {
  --bg:          #f5f4f0;
  --bg-elev:     #eeece7;
  --bg-elev-2:   #e6e4df;
  --bg-soft:     rgba(0,0,0,.04);
  --line:        rgba(0,0,0,.08);
  --line-strong: rgba(0,0,0,.13);
  --text:        #17191c;
  --muted:       #586170;
  --muted-2:     #7f8896;
  --cyan:        #009fc7;
  --cyan-soft:   rgba(0,159,199,.12);
  --cyan-soft-2: rgba(0,159,199,.18);
  --cyan-label:  rgba(0,159,199,.52);
  --green:       #0c9b6d;
  --green-soft:  rgba(12,155,109,.10);
  --amber:       #c78000;
  --amber-soft:  rgba(199,128,0,.10);
  --red:         #d4485e;
  --red-soft:    rgba(212,72,94,.10);
  --blue:        #347de6;
  --blue-soft:   rgba(52,125,230,.10);
  --purple:      #7c3aed;
  --glow:        0 0 0 3px rgba(0,159,199,.22);
  --shadow-sm:   0 2px 8px rgba(16,36,54,.08);
  --shadow-md:   0 8px 24px rgba(16,36,54,.12);
  --shadow-lg:   0 16px 32px rgba(16,36,54,.16);
}

/* tokens soft no definidos en styles.css — locales */
:root{
  --green-soft: rgba(0,196,140,.12);
  --amber-soft: rgba(246,166,35,.12);
  --red-soft:   rgba(242,95,92,.12);
  --blue-soft:  rgba(122,183,255,.10);
}
[data-theme="light"]{
  --green-soft: rgba(12,155,109,.10);
  --amber-soft: rgba(199,128,0,.10);
  --red-soft:   rgba(212,72,94,.10);
  --blue-soft:  rgba(52,125,230,.10);
}
}

*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html{overflow-x:clip}body{overflow-x:clip;font-family:var(--sans);background:radial-gradient(circle at 72% 8%, rgba(0,204,255,.07), transparent 28%),radial-gradient(circle at 12% 60%, rgba(0,204,255,.04), transparent 22%),linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.018) 1px, transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,.018) 1px, transparent 1px),var(--bg);background-size:auto,auto,52px 52px,52px 52px,auto;color:var(--text);line-height:1.5;font-size:14px;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased}html[data-theme="light"] body{background:radial-gradient(circle at 72% 8%, rgba(0,159,199,.06), transparent 28%),radial-gradient(circle at 12% 60%, rgba(0,159,199,.04), transparent 22%),linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.032) 1px, transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,.032) 1px, transparent 1px),var(--bg);background-size:auto,auto,52px 52px,52px 52px,auto}
a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
button{font:inherit;cursor:pointer;border:none;background:none}
::-webkit-scrollbar{width:5px;height:5px}
::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:transparent}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:rgba(127,136,150,.18);border-radius:999px}
@keyframes fadeInUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(6px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:.45}}

/* ── TOKENS ── */
.panel-kicker{font:700 10px var(--mono);letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--cyan);margin-bottom:5px;display:block}
.badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:5px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:var(--radius-pill);font:600 11px var(--mono);border:1px solid transparent}
.badge-cyan{background:var(--cyan-soft);color:var(--cyan);border-color:rgba(0,204,255,.22)}
.badge-amber{background:var(--amber-soft);color:var(--amber);border-color:rgba(255,176,32,.22)}
.badge-muted{background:var(--bg-soft);color:var(--muted-2);border-color:var(--line)}



/* ── HERO ── */
.hero{max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:72px 24px 56px;text-align:left;animation:fadeInUp .35s ease both}
.hero-kicker{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;padding:4px 10px;border-radius:var(--radius-pill);background:var(--cyan-soft);color:var(--cyan);font:700 10px var(--mono);letter-spacing:.10em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:20px;border:none}
.hero-title{font:800 clamp(32px,5vw,52px)/1.1 var(--display);letter-spacing:-.03em;margin-bottom:14px}
.hero-title span{color:inherit}
.hero-sub{color:var(--muted);font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;max-width:640px;margin-bottom:24px}
.hero-sub strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:600}

/* Search */

.search-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;max-width:640px}
.count-badge{flex-shrink:0;font:600 11px var(--mono);color:var(--muted-2);letter-spacing:.04em;white-space:nowrap}

/* ── CONTENT ── */
.content{max-width:1100px;margin:0 auto;padding:28px 24px 60px}

/* Info box — colapsable */
.info-box{box-shadow:0 0 0 1px rgba(0,204,255,.22);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);background:var(--bg-elev-2);margin-bottom:8px;overflow:hidden;animation:fadeInUp .35s .05s ease both}
.info-box-header{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:14px 20px;cursor:pointer;transition:background 180ms ease;gap:12px;user-select:none}
.info-box-header:hover{background:var(--bg-soft)}
.info-box-left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.info-box-left svg{width:15px;height:15px;stroke:var(--cyan);fill:none;stroke-width:1.8;flex-shrink:0;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round}
.info-box-label{font:700 12px var(--mono);color:var(--cyan);letter-spacing:.04em}
.info-box-chevron{width:15px;height:15px;stroke:var(--muted-2);fill:none;stroke-width:1.8;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;transition:transform 200ms ease;flex-shrink:0}
.info-box.open .info-box-chevron{transform:rotate(90deg)}
.info-box-body{display:none;padding:0 20px 18px;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
.info-box.open .info-box-body{display:block}
.info-body{font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.7;padding-top:14px}
.info-body p+p{margin-top:10px}
.info-body strong{color:var(--text);font-weight:600}
.info-steps{margin:10px 0 10px 18px;list-style:decimal;color:var(--muted);line-height:2.2}
.info-steps li strong{color:var(--text)}
.info-link{color:var(--cyan);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;text-decoration-color:rgba(0,204,255,.35);font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px}
.info-link:hover{text-decoration-color:var(--cyan)}
code{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;background:var(--bg-soft);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--line);padding:2px 7px;border-radius:var(--radius-xs);color:var(--cyan)}

/* ── SECTION HEAD ── */
.section-head{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:14px}
.section-title{font:700 9px var(--mono);letter-spacing:.16em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted-2)}

/* ── MODULE GRID ── */
.module-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(300px,1fr));gap:10px}

/* ── MODULE CARD ── */
.mod-card{background:var(--bg-elev-2);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius-lg);overflow:hidden;animation:fadeInUp .3s ease both;transition:box-shadow 180ms ease}
.mod-card.security{box-shadow:0 0 0 1px rgba(255,176,32,.18)}
.mod-card:hover{box-shadow:0 0 0 1px rgba(0,204,255,.28)}
.mod-card.security:hover{box-shadow:0 0 0 1px rgba(255,176,32,.38)}

.mod-card-header{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;padding:14px 16px;cursor:pointer;user-select:none;transition:background 180ms ease}
.mod-card-header:hover{background:var(--bg-soft)}
.mod-icon{width:34px;height:34px;border-radius:var(--radius-sm);flex-shrink:0;display:grid;place-items:center;background:var(--cyan-soft);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px rgba(0,204,255,.18);color:var(--cyan)}
.mod-icon svg{width:15px;height:15px;stroke:currentColor;fill:none;stroke-width:1.8;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round}
.mod-card.security .mod-icon{background:var(--amber-soft);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px rgba(255,176,32,.22);color:var(--amber)}
.mod-name{font:700 13px var(--sans);color:var(--text);flex:1;min-width:0}
.mod-chevron{width:14px;height:14px;stroke:var(--muted-2);fill:none;stroke-width:1.8;stroke-linecap:round;stroke-linejoin:round;transition:transform 200ms ease;flex-shrink:0}
.mod-card.open .mod-chevron{transform:rotate(90deg)}

.mod-body{display:none;padding:0 16px 16px;border-top:1px solid var(--line)}
.mod-card.open .mod-body{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px}
.mod-desc{font:400 12px var(--sans);color:var(--muted);line-height:1.55;padding-top:12px}
.mod-action{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;align-self:flex-start;text-decoration:none;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:var(--radius-pill);font:700 11px var(--mono);letter-spacing:.04em;color:var(--cyan);background:var(--cyan-soft);transition:all 180ms ease}
.mod-action:hover{background:var(--cyan-soft-2)}
.mod-card.security .mod-action{color:var(--amber);background:var(--amber-soft)}
.mod-card.security .mod-action:hover{background:rgba(255,176,32,.18)}

/* Empty state */
.empty-state{display:none;grid-column:1/-1;padding:40px 24px;text-align:center;color:var(--muted);border:1px dashed var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius-lg)}
.empty-state.show{display:block}


/* Delay per card */
.mod-card:nth-child(1){animation-delay:.04s}.mod-card:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.07s}
.mod-card:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.10s}.mod-card:nth-child(4){animation-delay:.13s}
.mod-card:nth-child(5){animation-delay:.16s}.mod-card:nth-child(6){animation-delay:.19s}
.mod-card:nth-child(7){animation-delay:.22s}.mod-card:nth-child(8){animation-delay:.25s}
.mod-card:nth-child(9){animation-delay:.28s}.mod-card:nth-child(10){animation-delay:.31s}
.mod-card:nth-child(11){animation-delay:.34s}.mod-card:nth-child(12){animation-delay:.37s}
.mod-card:nth-child(13){animation-delay:.40s}.mod-card:nth-child(14){animation-delay:.43s}
.mod-card:nth-child(15){animation-delay:.46s}.mod-card:nth-child(16){animation-delay:.49s}

@media(max-width:768px){
  .hero{padding:48px 16px 40px}
  .content{padding:20px 16px 48px}
  .module-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
}



/* ── MOBILE FIXES ── */
@media(max-width:640px){
  /* Search row: los botones bajan a segunda fila */
  .search-row{flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px}
  .search-row .search-wrap{flex:1 1 auto;min-width:0}
  .search-row #llmBtn,
  .search-row>a{
    flex:1 1 calc(50% - 4px);
    flex-shrink:1!important;
    justify-content:center;
    white-space:normal!important;
    text-align:center;
  }
  /* Info boxes: menos padding lateral */
  .info-box-header{padding:12px 14px;gap:8px}
  .info-box-body{padding:0 14px 16px}
  .info-box-label{letter-spacing:.02em}
}

@media(max-width:420px){
  /* Pantallas muy chicas: botones apilados */
  .search-row #llmBtn,
  .search-row>a{
    flex:1 1 100%;
    flex-shrink:1!important;
    justify-content:center;
  }
  /* Info box label más pequeño para que no apriete */
  .info-box-label{font-size:11px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<site-header base="./" current-page="api-docs"></site-header>

<!-- HERO -->
<div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-kicker"><svg width="11" height="11" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg> API Docs</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Índice de APIs de YiQi ERP</h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Módulos funcionales y especificaciones OpenAPI. Busca por tema y abre el Swagger de cada módulo.</p>
    <div class="search-row">
      <div class="search-wrap">
        <svg class="search-icon" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><circle cx="112" cy="112" r="80" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" fill="none"/><line x1="168" y1="168" x2="224" y2="224" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
        <input class="search-input" id="apiSearch" type="search" placeholder="Buscar módulo (ej: ventas, stock, auth…)" oninput="filterCards(this.value)"/>
      </div>
      <button id="llmBtn" onclick="copyForLLM()" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:0 14px;height:40px;border-radius:var(--radius);border:none;background:var(--bg-elev-2);color:var(--muted);font:600 11px var(--mono);letter-spacing:.04em;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;transition:all 180ms ease;flex-shrink:0"
        onmouseenter="this.style.color='var(--cyan)';this.style.background='var(--cyan-soft)'"
        onmouseleave="this.style.color='var(--muted)';this.style.background='var(--bg-elev-2)'">
        Copiar para LLMs
      </button>
      <a href="https://apidoc.yiqi.com.ar/modules.json" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:0 14px;height:40px;border-radius:var(--radius);border:none;background:var(--bg-elev-2);color:var(--muted);font:600 11px var(--mono);letter-spacing:.04em;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap;transition:all 180ms ease;flex-shrink:0;text-decoration:none"
        onmouseenter="this.style.color='var(--cyan)';this.style.background='var(--cyan-soft)'"
        onmouseleave="this.style.color='var(--muted)';this.style.background='var(--bg-elev-2)'">
        <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="8 17 12 21 16 17"/><line x1="12" y1="12" x2="12" y2="21"/><path d="M20.88 18.09A5 5 0 0 0 18 9h-1.26A8 8 0 1 0 3 16.29"/></svg>
        Catálogo JSON
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- CONTENT -->
<main class="content">

  <!-- Info box — colapsada por defecto -->
  <div class="info-box" id="infoBox">
    <div class="info-box-header" onclick="toggleInfo()">
      <div class="info-box-left">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 256 256"><circle cx="128" cy="128" r="96" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" fill="none"/><line x1="128" y1="120" x2="128" y2="176" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="128" cy="88" r="10" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
        <span class="info-box-label">Cómo usar esta documentación</span>
      </div>
      <svg class="info-box-chevron" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><polyline points="96 48 176 128 96 208" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" fill="none"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="info-box-body">
      <div class="info-body">
        <p><strong>Autenticación general:</strong> en <em>Seguridad</em> hay un único endpoint para obtener el token usando un usuario de YiQi. Este token se reutiliza en el resto de los módulos enviándolo como <code>Bearer</code> en el header <code>Authorization</code>.</p>
        <p><strong>Política de sesión:</strong> actualmente no hay refresh token. Cuando el token expira, se debe volver a autenticar con <code>/token</code>.</p>
        <ol class="info-steps">
          <li>Obtén el token desde el módulo <strong>Seguridad</strong>.</li>
          <li>Ejecuta <strong>GetLoginInformation</strong> como healthcheck canónico post-login.</li>
          <li>Toma <strong>schemaid</strong> desde esa respuesta (método primario).</li>
          <li>Elige un módulo desde el índice y abre su Swagger.</li>
          <li>Dentro del Swagger, expande las operaciones por tag.</li>
          <li>Valida los parámetros obligatorios, cuerpos de request y respuestas.</li>
        </ol>
        <p><strong>Estructura común de los Swagger:</strong> la mayoría de entidades siguen un formato homogéneo (operaciones list/get/create/update/delete, payloads con estructura repetida y respuestas paginadas o de detalle). Si entendés un módulo, la curva de adopción del resto suele ser mucho más rápida.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:10px">Para bots y agentes: consumí <a class="info-link" href="https://apidoc.yiqi.com.ar/modules.json" target="_blank" rel="noopener">modules.json</a> para descubrir el catálogo de specs de manera estructurada.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Info box 2 — Generalidades de endpoints -->
  <div class="info-box" id="infoBox2" style="border-color:rgba(0,204,255,.14);margin-bottom:8px">
    <div class="info-box-header" onclick="this.closest('.info-box').classList.toggle('open')">
      <div class="info-box-left">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 256 256"><polyline points="64 88 16 128 64 168" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/><polyline points="192 88 240 128 192 168" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/><line x1="160" y1="40" x2="96" y2="216" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" stroke-linecap="round" fill="none"/></svg>
        <span class="info-box-label">Generalidades de endpoints por entidad</span>
      </div>
      <svg class="info-box-chevron" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><polyline points="96 48 176 128 96 208" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" fill="none"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="info-box-body">
      <div class="info-body">
        <p>En los Swagger de YiQi, las entidades repiten un <strong>patrón de endpoints</strong>. Si aprendés el de una entidad, podés reutilizar el mismo enfoque en casi todas.</p>
        <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:10px;margin-top:14px">
          <div style="padding:12px 14px;background:var(--bg-soft);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius-sm)">
            <code style="color:var(--green)">GET /entidad/search</code>
            <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.55"><strong style="color:var(--text)">Búsqueda filtrada</strong> por atributos de la entidad. Suele devolver hasta <strong style="color:var(--text)">50 registros máximo</strong> por request.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:12px 14px;background:var(--bg-soft);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius-sm)">
            <code style="color:var(--cyan)">GET /entidad/{id}</code>
            <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.55"><strong style="color:var(--text)">Detalle</strong> de una instancia puntual. Requiere el <strong style="color:var(--text)">id</strong> en path.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:12px 14px;background:var(--bg-soft);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius-sm)">
            <code style="color:var(--amber)">POST /entidad</code>
            <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.55"><strong style="color:var(--text)">Alta</strong> de instancia. El body incluye <strong style="color:var(--text)">schemaid</strong> y un objeto <strong style="color:var(--text)">data</strong>.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:12px 14px;background:var(--bg-soft);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius-sm)">
            <code style="color:var(--blue)">PUT /entidad/{id}</code>
            <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.55"><strong style="color:var(--text)">Actualización</strong> de instancia existente, con estructura similar al alta.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:12px 14px;background:var(--bg-soft);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius-sm)">
            <code style="color:var(--red)">DELETE /entidad/{id}</code>
            <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.55"><strong style="color:var(--text)">Baja lógica/física</strong> según comportamiento de la entidad y reglas de negocio.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:12px 14px;background:var(--bg-soft);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius-sm)">
            <code style="color:var(--cyan)">GET /entidad/smartie</code>
            <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.55"><strong style="color:var(--text)">Vista (smartie) paginada.</strong> Un smartie es un reporte/vista armado por usuarios sobre la entidad.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:12px 14px;background:var(--bg-soft);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius-sm)">
            <code style="color:var(--amber)">POST /entidad/changestate</code>
            <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.55"><strong style="color:var(--text)">Cambio de estado</strong> de workflow (cuando la entidad maneja estados).</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:12px 14px;background:var(--bg-soft);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius-sm)">
            <code style="color:var(--purple)">GET|PUT /entidad/file</code>
            <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.55"><strong style="color:var(--text)">Descarga/carga de archivos</strong> asociados a atributos de tipo archivo.</p>
          </div>
          <div style="padding:12px 14px;background:var(--bg-soft);box-shadow:0 0 0 1px var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius-sm)">
            <code style="color:var(--green)">GET /entidad/report</code>
            <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);margin-top:6px;line-height:1.55"><strong style="color:var(--text)">Descarga de reportes</strong> predefinidos (por ejemplo PDFs) para una instancia.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Info box 3 — Buena práctica para consumir smarties -->
  <div class="info-box" style="border-color:rgba(21,212,156,.22);margin-bottom:8px">
    <div class="info-box-header" onclick="this.closest('.info-box').classList.toggle('open')">
      <div class="info-box-left">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 256 256"><polyline points="40 144 96 200 224 64" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" fill="none"/></svg>
        <span class="info-box-label" style="color:var(--green)">Buena práctica para consumir smarties</span>
      </div>
      <svg class="info-box-chevron" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><polyline points="96 48 176 128 96 208" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" fill="none"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="info-box-body">
      <div class="info-body">
        <p><strong>Orden recomendado:</strong> ordenar por <strong>fecha de modificación descendente</strong> para traer primero lo más reciente.</p>
        <p><strong>Estrategia de paginado eficiente:</strong> paginar desde <code>page=1</code> y detenerse cuando se alcance la <strong>última fecha ya sincronizada</strong> por tu proceso.</p>
        <p><strong>Objetivo:</strong> evitar paginado exhaustivo innecesario, reducir tráfico y proteger el rendimiento general del sistema.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Info box 4 — Uso responsable de la API -->
  <div class="info-box" style="border-color:rgba(255,176,32,.22);margin-bottom:24px">
    <div class="info-box-header" onclick="this.closest('.info-box').classList.toggle('open')">
      <div class="info-box-left">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 256 256"><path d="M142.74,40l93.19,160A16,16,0,0,1,222.19,224H33.81A16,16,0,0,1,20.07,200l93.19-160A16,16,0,0,1,142.74,40Z" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" fill="none"/><line x1="128" y1="136" x2="128" y2="104" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="128" cy="168" r="10" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
        <span class="info-box-label" style="color:var(--amber)">Uso responsable de la API</span>
      </div>
      <svg class="info-box-chevron" viewBox="0 0 256 256"><polyline points="96 48 176 128 96 208" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="18" fill="none"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="info-box-body">
      <div class="info-body">
        <p><strong>Responsabilidad de uso:</strong> el consumo de la API debe realizarse con criterios de eficiencia, control de volumen y frecuencia de llamadas.</p>
        <p><strong>Riesgos operativos:</strong> un uso intensivo o sin límites puede saturar tráfico, degradar tiempos de respuesta y afectar a otros usuarios.</p>
        <p><strong>Cuenta técnica recomendada:</strong> utilizar usuarios de API con el <strong>menor privilegio posible</strong>, otorgando solo permisos estrictamente necesarios.</p>
        <p><strong>Riesgo asumido por el integrador:</strong> la implementación, su impacto operativo y los riesgos asociados son responsabilidad del usuario que consume la API.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
